summary: I went to a netball hearing today as a witness after a girl headbutted my friend in a game. My friend had two black eyes and a...
body: I went to a netball hearing today as a witness after a girl headbutted my friend in a game. My friend had two black eyes and a swollen nose and the girl quite clearly did it deliberately but the board said they won’t do anything because we didn’t have permission to take footage of the game and our statements did not match the other girls. I am honestly sooooo angry. Not only did I waste an evening where they did not care about my word but also the girl got away with it….she did not even have to write an apology to my friend.
